In this article, Melania Trump reflects on her role as the First Lady and her commitment to helping children through her BE BEST initiative. She criticizes the media for focusing on salacious claims made by a former contractor who she believes is seeking personal gain. Melania emphasizes the importance of staying focused on the positive work being done to support children and urges the media to prioritize the next generation. She expresses gratitude for the support she has received and looks forward to continuing her work over the next four years.